00:41:06,266 --> 00:41:07,934
"Alamat: Yeonbuk-ro 63-gil 29, B1. Apartemen semibasemen"

528
00:41:20,080 --> 00:41:22,015
"Komentar Terbaik: Memalukan. Komentar Teratas: Serang rumahnya"

